\v 3 Se <a name="02100600300006">alguém</a> <a name="02100600300004" ll="SDBH:ילד:000001" il="Baby_boy_after_birth;Birth;Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan">gerar</a> <a name="02100600300008" ll="SDBH:מֵאָה:000000">cem</a> filhos e <a name="02100600300016" ll="SDBH:חיה:000000">viver</a> <a name="02100600300014" ll="SDBH:רַב:000001">muitos</a> <a name="02100600300012" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">anos</a>, até <a name="02100600300020" ll="SDBH:רַב:000001">avançada</a> <a name="02100600300026;02100600300028" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000004;SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">idade</a>, e se a <a name="02100600300032" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">sua</a> <a name="02100600300032" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">alma</a> não <a name="02100600300036" ll="SDBH:שׂבע:000006">se</a> <a name="02100600300036" ll="SDBH:שׂבע:000006">fartar</a> do <a name="02100600300042" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000003">bem</a>, e além disso não tiver <a name="02100600300048" ll="SDBH:קְבוּרָה:000000" il="Bolen00090;Tombs-rock-cut;tb110800210">sepultura</a>, <a name="02100600300056" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">digo</a> que um <a name="02100600300064" ll="SDBH:נֵפֶל:000000">aborto</a> é mais <a name="02100600300058" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000001">feliz</a> do que ele; 
