\v 6 <a name="02100600600004" ll="SDBH:אִלּוּ:000000">ainda</a> <a name="02100600600004" ll="SDBH:אִלּוּ:000000">que</a> aquele <a name="02100600600006" ll="SDBH:חיה:000000">vivesse</a> <a name="02100600600012">duas</a> <a name="02100600600012">vezes</a> <a name="02100600600008" ll="SDBH:אֶלֶף:001000">mil</a> <a name="02100600600010" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">anos</a>, mas não <a name="02100600600020" ll="SDBH:ראה:000009">gozasse</a> o <a name="02100600600016" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000000">bem</a>. Porventura, não <a name="02100600600036" ll="SDBH:הלך:000007">vão</a> todos para o <a name="02100600600030" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">mesmo</a> <a name="02100600600028" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugar</a>?
    
