\v 9 <a name="02100600900002" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">Melhor</a> é a <a name="02100600900004" ll="SDBH:מַרְאֶה:000000">vista</a> dos <a name="02100600900006" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> do que o <a name="02100600900010" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">andar</a> <a name="02100600900010" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">ocioso</a> <a name="02100600900012" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">da</a> <a name="02100600900012" ll="SDBH:נֶפֶשׁ:000001">cobiça</a>; também isto é <a name="02100600900018" ll="SDBH:הֶבֶל:000002">vaidade</a> e <a name="02100600900022" ll="SDBH:רְעוּת:001000">correr</a> <a name="02100600900022" ll="SDBH:רְעוּת:001000">atrás</a> do <a name="02100600900024" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000004" il="Gale_Force_Winds">vento</a>.
    
